'''DXSJ-TV''' is a commercial television relay station owned by [[ABS-CBN Broadcasting Corporation]] with affiliation with Saint Jude Broadcasting Foundation. It's studio is located at Borromeo St., [[Surigao City]].
==ABS-CBN TV-12 Local Programs== *[[TV Patrol Caraga]] (simulcast on originating ABS-CBN TV-11 Butuan) *[[Silib to da Max]] (local lifestyle show of ABS-CBN Butuan)
==ABS-CBN TV-12 Personalities== * Richmond Hinayon (TV Patrol Caraga Anchor) ==Note== * *both stations (ABS-CBN and Studio 23) use the same amount of power.
